org.llrp.ltk.generated.custom.parameters

Class ImpinjTagReportContentSelector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.llrp.ltk.types.LLRPParameter
      • org.llrp.ltk.types.TLVParameter
        • org.llrp.ltk.generated.parameters.Custom
          • org.llrp.ltk.generated.custom.parameters.ImpinjTagReportContentSelector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccessCommandOpSpec, AccessCommandOpSpecResult, SpecParameter

    public class ImpinjTagReportContentSelector
extends Custom
    This custom parameter configures additional parameters to be reported via the TagReportData parameter. Each optional parameter individually enables/configures a particular feature. Note that because of how the ROReportSpec parameter is handled (see section 3.1.15), if the optional parameter used to control a particular feature is absent, the feature is considered disabled. See the documentation for the actual parameters for full feature descriptions. See also
